<h2>Application Configuration</h2>
<hr/>

<br/>
<p>
Leave blank if you are testing EcomPages on your local machine, such as <span style="color:green;">127.0.0.1:3000</span>. <br/><br/>
Leave blank if EcomPages can be accessed from <span style="color:green;">www.yourdoamin.com</span>. <br/><br/>
If EcomPages is accessed from <span style="color:green;">www.yourdoamin.com/shop/</span>, then you need to put <span style="color:green;">/shop</span> into the field below.
<p>
